                <p rend="flushleft">I <hi rend="italic">Forthcoming Work of the Council</hi>
                </p>
                <p>It was agreed that the Ministers would hold two meetings on July 12, the first
                    being fixed for 12:00 noon, the next meeting of the Deputies to be held July 12
                    at 9:00 a.m.</p>
                <p rend="flushleft">II <hi rend="italic">Germany</hi>
                </p>
                <p>The Ministers continued their exchange of views on the German question.</p>
                <pb facs="0923" n="899" xml:id="pg_899"/>
                <p>They decided to hold a special session of the Council of Foreign Ministers
                    devoted to the German question after the close of the General Assembly of the
                    United Nations.</p>
